value.name: Convert date format from 20180-01-01 to 201801 - Stack Overflow
value.snippet: 201801 is not a complete date, provided the 2018 is the year. In any case datetime has no format, so there is nothing to change. If you are storing dates in a varchar column, then please don't. – GSerg Sep 26, 2019 at 8:47 1 This is something you probably want to be doing in the presentation layer, not the data layer. – Diado Sep 26, 2019 at 8:49
